GIT Class -3


TOPIC: GIT AMEND, GIT REVERT & GIT BRANCHES
=============================================

* yum install git -y    -----------------------------> command to install git
* git init              -----------------------------> command to initialize the git
* git add *             -----------------------------> command to commit all files at a time


There is a possible way to change the author name for the recent commit (recent last commit only) by using AMEND command like below

* git commit --amend --author "pranay <gorantlapranay8@gmail.com>"     -------------------> command to change the author name for the recent commit (recent last commit only) by using AMEND command
after hitting the above command one file will open like below

myntra file

# Please enter the commit message for your changes. Lines starting
